//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.1     -- 2004-03-23
First public Release.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.1.1   -- 2004-03-27
Added "Enter" key event to translate with enter key.
Prints "Phrase not found" message when not found in DB.
Minor improvements in message dialogs.
Installation script now checks for "root" user and existing installation.
Added "TODO", "README" and  "changelog"  files.
Some code clean up.
Compiled with wxGTK 2.4.2.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.2.0    -- 2004-04-02
Application is now completely XML based. wxsqlite/sqlite removed! :-)
Input text control now has focus, so user does not need to click on it.
Toolbar added.
XML DB navigation added.
Many many small improvements and bug fixes.
Some Code clean up.
Updated  installation script.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.2.1   -- 2004-04-07
Word cache added. It stores 15 recent searched words.
Auto-Translate for cached words added.
Some toolbar icon changed.
Segmentation fault error on application exit solved.
Installation script minor updates.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.2.2   -- 2004-04-17
Auto Select word feature added.
Toolbar updated.
Main window size changed.
About dialog size changed.
Parse error bug solved.
Auto button OnClick() bug solved.
Standard configure/make system added to source code
(Thanks to Arash Bijanzadeh <a.bijanzadeh@linuxiran.org>)
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.3.0   -- 2004-04-23
Settings dialog/Configuration file added.
Auto select feature improved.
Auto translate option removed and it's now active by default.
Toolbar texts removed and new tools added.
Copy/Paste/Cut functions added. Copy function copies result to clipboard
Error Dialogs improved.
Added Icons to menus.
No external images are used anymore. All images are included as xpm.
LibPNG is not used anymore.
Installer minor updates.
Word cache and window position saving/restore.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.3.1   -- 2004-05-07
Clear hostory feature added.
GCC 3.3 and above compile error solved. (thanks to Arash Bijanzadeh)
History limit exceeding bug solved.
Invalid document bug on empty cache restore solved.
Updated some toolbar/menu icons.
Traditional installer removed. Now we offer Debian/RPM/Slackware
binary packages.
Some code clean up.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.3.2   -- 2004-08-20
GCC 3.3 and above compile error on some distros solved. (tested with GCC 3.3.4)
Again(!) history limit exceeding bug solved.
Nuvola icon set.
Main window size changed.
Some code clean up.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.4.0   -- 2004-10-01
Finally, History cache works w/o any problem. 
User can change result box font face/size.
Search for Similar Word feature added.
Minor fixes in application GUI design.
Size of About window change to be displayed correctly on some distros like SuSE.
Some updates in Icons.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.4.1   -- 2004-10-15
2 Bugs in Auto Search menu and Settings restore solved.
Toggle On/Off toolbar feature added.
Some minor fixes in GUI.
Some improvements in Search for Similar word function. Now can add "e" to the end of words and can
detect -ing, -tion words to search faster.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.4.2   -- 2004-11-15
View Toolbar is default on.
Ctrl+V conflict solved.
SFS (Search For Similar) function is restricted to <=20 char words to avoid program over load.
Compile problem in Fedora/Slackware solved, but link error on Unicode wxGTK still is a problem.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
0.4.3   -- 2004-11-24
All options are active by default. 
Many improvements in source package scripts, thanks to Zoup.
User can set XML DB path from Settings window. Also it's possible to put XML DB in a web server.
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
