First version using wxGTK 2.5.3.
This version fixes runtime/compile time gtk accel errors on some distros.
Added Taskbar icon and popup menu.
Added Paste and Translate feature.
Busy cursur during database search.
Set XML DB directory dialog added.
Some icon updates and GTK+ stock icons for buttons.
Some bug fixes like auto translate history cache related bug.
Some updates in Settings and About windows.
